 Cart\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"e759839acdae\",{\"children\":[\"Imagine adding a product to your cart, only to find additional items have been automatically included without your consent. This underhanded tactic may lead to higher sales in the short term, but it ultimately damages the user experience and erodes trust.\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"b76bd51c45c6\",{\"children\":[\"Alternative: Prioritize user choice and consent. Allow customers to add or remove products from their cart with ease. If you want to suggest additional items, make it clear that they are optional and require the user to actively select them. This approach maintains customer autonomy and fosters a positive shopping experience.\"]}],[\"$\",\"h2\",\"0da0b37d613f\",{\"className\":\"text-[2vw] font-medium my-4\",\"children\":[\"Charges Should Come with a Notification\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"bbf2e4db043f\",{\"children\":[\"Hidden fees and unexpected charges are not only frustrating but can also lead to a loss of customer trust. Transparency in pricing is essential to maintaining a positive user experience and building long-term customer loyalty.\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"b289c23cc8c3\",{\"children\":[\"Alternative: Disclose all fees and charges upfront. Provide a clear breakdown of costs during the checkout process, including taxes, shipping fees, and any additional charges. This allows customers to make informed decisions and prevents unpleasant surprises when they review their order.\"]}],[\"$\",\"div\",\"4e3df6d66887\",{\"className\":\"my-5 flex items-center justify-center h-[35vw] tablet:w-full tablet:h-auto\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L1c\",null,{\"src\":\"https://cdn.sanity.io/images/gzupotgr/production/f035097e39d842cff31a4f27c31729ff96326ddc-1024x576.webp\",\"alt\":\"unmasking-web-dark-2\",\"width\":800,\"height\":1000,\"className\":\"rounded-lg\"}]}],[\"$\",\"h2\",\"853a2139f510\",{\"className\":\"text-[2vw] font-medium my-4\",\"children\":[\"Copyblogger\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"a811f937a95f\",{\"children\":[\"Copyblogger